34:27.931 --> 34:30.467
But they couldn't get clear.

34:30.819 --> 34:32.339
What happened to them?

34:33.739 --> 34:35.609
Well, they had to leave.

34:36.824 --> 34:38.472
They left you here?

34:41.094 --> 34:43.916
