35:09.257 --> 35:11.987
I want to fight it.

35:12.926 --> 35:14.777
Okay.

35:36.817 --> 35:38.387
Jesus.

35:40.855 --> 35:43.233
Let's go for a walk.

35:55.436 --> 35:58.026
So you ever shot anything before?

35:59.039 --> 36:03.141
No. Guns aren't really my sort of thing.

36:03.778 --> 36:07.382
There was this one time
when I was guarding a checkpoint.

36:07.682 --> 36:10.495
