a vest with a bomb on it.

36:27.436 --> 36:30.639
And he's walking towards us with this...

36:30.739 --> 36:35.053
this stupid fucking grin on his face.

36:35.153 --> 36:38.847
And we're all screaming at him
and people are running everywhere,

36:38.947 --> 36:41.116
women, little kids.

36:41.216 --> 36:46.455
But this guy... man, this guy,
he was as cool as they come.

36:47.155 --> 36:49.391
My sergeant, he's there,
he's yelling at me,

36:49.491 --> 36:52.623
"take him down, take him down!"

36:53.295 --> 36:55.230
Problem was...

36:55.330 --> 36:58.133
I'd never actually shot anyone before.

36:58.233 --> 37:02.103
So obviously I was shitting myself,
I had the shakes, had the sweats,

37:02.203 --> 37:06.374
all the usual things you get when you've
been told to shoot a guy dead.

37:06.474 --> 37:07.836
Yeah.

37:07.936 --> 37:12.150
So they're still barking at me,
telling me to shoot this guy.

37:12.250 --> 37:17.174
And he's getting closer and closer
with this stupid fucking grin.

37:18.053 --> 37:20.565
So I'm lying there in the dirt...

37:20.665 --> 37:23.959
looking at this bloke
through the scope of my gun...

37:24.359 --> 37:26.665
and it suddenly dawns on me...

37:26.765 --> 37:30.916
that this guy... he actually wants to die.

37:32.833 --> 37:34.916
There you go.

37:40.174 --> 37:42.667
- Sorry.
- Nah, that's alright.

37:43.210 --> 37:45.163
What happened to him?

37:45.263 --> 37:48.141
Yep, I killed him.

37:48.750 --> 37:50.921
Through and through.

37:51.386 --> 37:53.969
Big fucking mess.

37:55.656 --> 37:59.803
But we found out later... he was crazy.

37:59.903 --> 38:03.565
He'd just lost his wife and his kid.

38:03.665 --> 38:06.163
Didn't have a bomb on him.

38:06.263 --> 38:08.810
Just wanted to get shot.

38:10.738 --> 38:12.568
Well...

38:14.136 --> 38:18.046
- What happened to you?
- Gave me a medal.

38:18.146 --> 38:20.625
I went to Thailand.

38:20.725 --> 38:22.884
Got hooked on smack.

38:22.984 --> 38:27.677
I fucked a lot. Forgot who I was
for about three years.

38:28.657 --> 38:31.147
And I came back here...

38:32.610 --> 38:34.813
I got clean...

38:35.363 --> 38:37.778
and I built this place.

38:43.621 --> 38:45.748
Anything else you want to know?

38:49.964 --> 38:52.614
This is the beginning of your healing.

38:53.064 --> 38:54.483
You understand?

38:54.783 --> 38:56.951
- Yes, Father.
- You?

38:57.051 --> 39:01.353
It's just... I'm so fucking exhausted
I can... What's the question again?

39:01.453 --> 39:04.125
You land on our doorstep
and expect us to rescue you,

39:04.225 --> 39:06.928
you have to be prepared
to go the whole journey.

39:07.028 --> 39:09.141
It's not enough for us
that you're not dead.

39:10.065 --> 39:13.612
There's a few very basic rules.
You eat what you're given.

39:13.712 --> 39:17.906
You do the drills without holding back and
you work with the others in the community.

39:18.006 --> 39:22.900
And you only talk about
what you feel to me or Tom.

39:23.311 --> 39:26.329
- That clear?
- Yes, Father.

39:27.765 --> 39:29.631
Yeah.

39:30.684 --> 39:33.100
Show us your strength.

39:35.132 --> 39:37.605
- You've gotta be kidding me.
- Come on, you're weak.

39:37.705 --> 39:40.263
- Shut up, Marcus.
- Hit it, Travis.

39:40.463 --> 39:43.084
Listen, I think that this
is getting a bit out of hand.

39:43.184 --> 39:46.202
- Hit the bag!
- Just hit the bag, mate.

39:46.302 --> 39:48.587
- Just hit the bag?
- Just hit the bag.

39:48.687 --> 39:51.489
- Hit the bag.
- Hit the fucking bag.

39:51.589 --> 39:54.576
- Hit the fucking bag.
- Hit the bag! Just hit it!

39:54.676 --> 39:56.952
- Hit the bag!
- Hit it, Travis!

39:57.052 --> 39:59.381
- Hit the bag.
- Come on, mate.

40:03.283 --> 40:06.500
I can't do it. I'm not doing this.

40:09.507 --> 40:11.267
Go and get some rest, mate.

40:24.772 --> 40:27.075
I need something.

40:27.175 --> 40:28.944
I'm really sick.

40:29.444 --> 40:33.596
- Well, how about a run?
- That wasn't what I had in mind.

40:41.171 --> 40:43.258
To heal...

40:43.358 --> 40:45.127
all my injuries.

40:45.427 --> 40:47.619
To be safe.

40:48.019 --> 40:50.644
To feel safe with myself.

40:52.833 --> 40:56.485
To love... everyone. Equally.

40:59.107 --> 41:02.540
To find the joy in everything.
Even in pain.

41:02.660 --> 41:04.918
To be a protector of the community.

41:07.014 --> 41:08.917
To be powerful.

41:09.017 --> 41:12.798
So that nothing and no one
can harm our community.

41:13.338 --> 41:15.894
This is the purpose of my life.

41:16.491 --> 41:20.061
To touch people with music.
To show them the way out of their pain.

41:20.161 --> 41:22.024
Come on!

41:22.946 --> 41:25.363
To walk the red road in peace.

41:42.349 --> 41:44.651
- So what do you feel?
- I feel sick.

41:44.751 --> 41:47.322
That's because you're sick on the inside.

41:47.422 --> 41:49.357
That's what your body's showing you.

41:49.457 --> 41:54.262
You've been hiding behind your addiction
and you've been hurting yourself.

41:54.362 --> 41:58.066
But these feelings, it's just the advertising,
it's just the wrapping, yeah?

41:58.166 --> 42:02.237
I don't understand. I don't understand.
I don't understand what you're saying.

42:02.337 --> 42:05.294
- Do you get it?
- No, I don't get it.

42:06.356 --> 42:08.607
It's your soul.

42:10.010 --> 42:11.280
Do you get that?

42:11.880 --> 42:15.356
Hey, do you get it, do you fucking get it?

42:16.283 --> 42:19.135
- I think so.
- Then say it.

42:20.654 --> 42:24.527
- My soul...
- Your soul what?

42:25.393 --> 42:28.063
My soul is sick.

42:28.763 --> 42:31.887
My soul is in pain.

42:45.746 --> 42:47.949
See that's the tradeoff.

42:48.049 --> 42:51.592
Pain... for freedom.

43:02.896 --> 43:06.668
When I got back from Iraq,
I was a mess, man.

43:06.768 --> 43:08.903
I was a fucking mess.

43:09.003 --> 43:12.841
Thought I was gonna die soon,
so what's the point in living, yeah?

43:12.941 --> 43:17.846
Couldn't hold down a relationship.
Couldn't feel any emotions.

43:18.446 --> 43:21.794
And then one day, I had a good look around

43:21.894 --> 43:25.553
and I realized: Holy fucking shit!

43:25.653 --> 43:27.989
Everyone's doing the same thing.

43:28.089 --> 43:30.992
Everyone's terrified
of finding their own truth.

43:31.092 --> 43:34.129
And even more shit-scared
of doing anything about it.

43:34.229 --> 43:36.086
Yeah?

43:44.304 --> 43:47.048
Come on in, mate, it is fucking beautiful.

43:48.608 --> 43:50.532
Come on.

43:57.084 --> 43:59.130
So how do you feel?

44:01.121 --> 44:04.672
- I don't feel anything, really.
- Come on.

44:04.772 --> 44:07.509
Hey, you're alive, aren't you, man?

44:09.197 --> 44:11.533
You alive now? No?

44:11.633 --> 44:14.042
Okay, how about now?

44:14.142 --> 44:16.505
How about now? Now?

44:16.705 --> 44:18.440
